@startuml
start

:Customer places order;
:Waiter enters order into system;

if (Is order valid?) then (yes)
  :System records and confirms order;
  :Order sent to kitchen queue;
  :Kitchen prepares the meal;
  :Waiter serves the meal to customer;
  :Customer requests the bill;
  :Cashier processes payment;
  :System prints receipt;
  stop
else (no)
  :System alerts waiter of invalid entry;
  :Waiter corrects the order;
  -> loop back;
endif
@enduml